&lt;p&gt;Continuing the theme of &lt;a href="https://coders4climatestrike.com/2019/11/voting-with-your-wallet.html"&gt;voting with your wallet&lt;/a&gt;, how about switching to an ethical mobile network? &lt;a href="https://www.ecotalk.co.uk/"&gt;Ecotalk&lt;/a&gt;, a UK mobile (cell) network, achieved the highest score in the Nov/Dec 2019 &lt;a href="https://www.ethicalconsumer.org/"&gt;Ethical Consumer&lt;/a&gt; ratings.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.coders4climatestrike.com/2019/11/switching-to-an-ethical-phone-network.html?utm_source=ethical-phone&amp;amp;utm_medium=Atom"&gt;&lt;em&gt;More&amp;hellip;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</content></entry>
