&lt;p&gt;Do you want to do something now? A few interesting alternatives:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Buy a phone you can easily repair (a high level on the fairphone)&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Offset when you fly&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Reduce plastic at home and the office&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.coders4climatestrike.com/2019/11/voting-with-your-wallet.html?utm_source=ethical-phone&amp;amp;utm_medium=Atom"&gt;&lt;em&gt;More&amp;hellip;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</content></entry></feed>